 allow us to obtain statistical significances of the signal over the SM\nbackgrounds with values up to $\\sim$ 1.6$\\sigma$ and $\\sim$ 3$\\sigma$, for\ntotal integrated luminosities of 300 fb$^{-1}$ and 1000 fb$^{-1}$,\nrespectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Oct 2017 17:24:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Mar 2018 13:50:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-08"}
