aditional techniques that consider\nindividual variability indices or their linear combination. The NN, SGB, SVM\nand RF show a higher efficiency compared to LR and kNN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Oct 2017 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Jan 2018 16:50:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-25"}
