\nhigh-obliquity region allows for moderate variations, and all obliquities\ncorresponding to retrograde motion (i.e. $> 90^\\circ$) are stable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Oct 2017 18:09:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 May 2018 19:06:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
